  "bio_raw": "Nazmun Nur Eva has joined as Lecturer at ULAB in May, 2023.She has 4 years of full- time teaching experience as Lecturer and BBA program coordinator in two other private universities of Bangladesh. She also has corporate experience over 8.5+ years in different multinational companies of Bangladesh and UK. Her academic credential includes MBA in Business Management from Liverpool John Moores University, UK. She has also earned her Bachelors’ degree in HRM & Marketing from East West University, Dhaka, Bangladesh. With the motivation of the idea of blending the theoretical learning and corporate experience, she also has done Post Graduate Diploma in Management from Business college of London, UK. She is doing her MPhil in Strategic Management in Bangladesh University of Professionals, Dhaka, Bangladesh. She is interested to focus on the research area of strategic management analysis for sustainability , HRM issues, entrepreneurship, branding and consumer behavior.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Strategic HR & Marketing Management, Entrepreneurship, Training and Development, Branding, , consumer Behavior."
  ],
  "education": [
